headline: TKO Group Holdings (TKO): Evaluating Valuation After a Significant Fourth-Quarter Cash Dividend Announcement
summary: TKO Group Holdings (TKO) just put real cash on the table, declaring a fourth quarter dividend of 0.78 dollars per share that returns roughly 150 million dollars to Class A shareholders. See our latest analysis for TKO Group Holdings. The dividend news comes on top of strong recent momentum, with a 1 month share price return of 14.43 percent and a year to date share price return of 47.59 percent, while the 1 year total shareholder return of 44.86 percent suggests investors have already been...
